 Being a company that listen, DARA BAKES N CAKES have unveiled a new exciting product,the Treasure Treat Box from 1 February 2022. Speaking on the development, Zainab Odukoya,Creative director of the company said “due to the increasing demands from the clients and the enquires from the public, we have decided to act on this demand.The product is specifically designed to give our customers experiential options to meet the market demand and appeal.THE TREASURE TREAT BOX has a combination of items from Dara’s Bakes N CAKES along with other elements and gifts that makes it truly a Box of treasures. Some MCSN Members Disappointed With Royalty Sharing Policy ‘Apes Obey,’ Story Of A Lagos Where Whites Never Mixed With The… The Treasure Treat Box, Odukoya said comes in three different types. The king-size Boxes the Big size and the Small size. The Treasure Treat Boxes,she said can be ordered for online while a physical pick up can also be explored. DARA BAKES N CAKES is a creative confection Business with top notch product and service designed to satisfy our clients needs with premium focus on quality service delivery.Over the years, Dara’s Bakes N Cakes has dedicated itself to developing solutions and products worthy of our clients and market.